  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth/v1.10.25-stable-69568c55/linux-amd64/go1.18.6\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\nSwitch to full syncmode.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\nStayed in snap syncmode\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\n\r\nSync in syncmode=snap then swith syncmode to full.\r\n\r\n#### Backtrace\r\n\r\n````\r\nINFO [09-21|13:16:29.445] Disk storage enabled for ethash caches   dir=/root/.ethereum/geth/ethash count=3\r\nINFO [09-21|13:16:29.445] Disk storage enabled for ethash DAGs     dir=/root/.ethash               count=2\r\nINFO [09-21|13:16:29.452] Initialising Ethereum protocol           network=1 dbversion=8\r\nINFO [09-21|13:16:29.479] Loaded most recent local header          number=15,579,937 hash=801b08..8bcfc2 td=58,750,003,716,598,352,816,469 age=7h9m30s\r\nINFO [09-21|13:16:29.480] Loaded most recent local full block      number=0          hash=d4e567..cb8fa3 td=17,179,869,184                 age=53y5mo3w\r\nINFO [09-21|13:16:29.480] Loaded most recent local fast block      number=15,579,937 hash=801b08..8bcfc2 td=58,750,003,716,598,352,816,469 age=7h9m30s\r\nINFO [09-21|13:16:29.483] Loaded last fast-sync pivot marker       number=15,581,878\r\nINFO [09-21|13:16:29.908] Loaded local transaction journal         transactions=0 dropped=0\r\nINFO [09-21|13:16:29.908] Regenerated local transaction journal    transactions=0 accounts=0\r\nWARN [09-21|13:16:29.908] Switch sync mode from full sync to snap sync\r\n````\r\n\r\nHow can i switch the mode as it was before?\r\nThanks!",
