    "body": "Switching from snap to syncmode=full is not supported. Or, rather, the way to do it is to do `geth removebd` (delete all current data) and do a new sync `geth ... syncmode=full` from scratch. \r\n\r\nWHen doing this, you can unfortunately _not_ keep the ancients intact, but must delete them too. Ideally, geth would just import them locally, but that has not been implemented :(  ",
